Patch 8.0.0839
Problem:    Cannot kill a job in a terminal with CTRL-C.
Solution:   Set the controlling tty and send SIGINT. (closes #1910)
Files:      src/os_unix.c, src/terminal.c, src/proto/os_unix.pro


